{"data":[{"date":"08:11 13/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Pakistan t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nguoi-pakistan-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pakistan k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau 3 n\u0103m nh\u1eadn l\u1ec7nh c\u1ea5m t\u1eeb FIFA.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pakistan, Syed Faisal Saleh Hayat \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Pakistan t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Pakistan t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Nguoi-Pakistan-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Pakistan t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;C\u00e1c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Brazil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 trong th\u1eddi gian qua \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao v\u00e0 m\u00e0i d\u0169a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Bahrain s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cho h\u1ecd, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Pakistan c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n 2 tu\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i Bahrain v\u1edbi hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Indonesia t\u1eeb t\u1ed1i 9/8, t\u1ee9c l\u00e0 s\u1edbm h\u01a1n 2 ng\u00e0y so v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i, HLV Jose Antonio Nogueir c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0: &ldquo;\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t v\u00ec gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t c\u1ea1nh tranh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-noi-gi-khi-bi-chu-nha-indonesia-gay-kho-de-168-194341.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-noi-gi-khi-bi-chu-nha-indonesia-gay-kho-de.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-noi-gi-khi-bi-chu-nha-indonesia-gay-kho-de-168-194341.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi b\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i gi\u1edd t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ph\u00eda n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc-168-194334.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc-168-194334.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5418","checkdouble":"194370"},{"date":"08:30 13/08","title":"N\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/nuoc-chu-nha-indonesia-len-tieng-sau-su-co-voi-dt-olympic-viet-nam.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ASIAD 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u00e2n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>N\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 12/8, bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch do ph\u00eda n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3 thay v\u00ec ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp l\u00fac 20h00, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1eadp \u2018chay\u2019 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u00ea t\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Untitled.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>N\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau nh\u1eefng sai s\u00f3t v\u1eeba qua</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc sai s\u00f3t n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n BTC Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00ec nh\u1eefng sai s\u00f3t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 trong th\u1eddi gian qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m cho bi\u1ebft: \"Ph\u00eda ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 xin l\u1ed7i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00ec c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 c\u1eadp r\u1eadp. D\u00f9 sao to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ee7y bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra sau khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00ednh to\u00e1n k\u0129 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n ch\u00fang ta t\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u00fac 8h t\u1ed1i. T\u1eadp xong m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n g\u1ea7n 50 c\u00e2y s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n th\u00ec s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D c\u00f9ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Nepal v\u00e0 Pakistan. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Pakistan ng\u00e0y 14/8 v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p Nepal hai ng\u00e0y sau. C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ba ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00f4m 19/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-pakistan-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194370.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nguoi-pakistan-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-pakistan-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194370.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Pakistan t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pakistan k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-tiep-tuc-bi-nuoc-chu-nha-indonesia-gay-kho-de-168-194336.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/olympic-viet-nam-tiep-tuc-bi-nuoc-chu-nha-indonesia-gay-kho-de.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-tiep-tuc-bi-nuoc-chu-nha-indonesia-gay-kho-de-168-194336.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 do b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5417","checkdouble":"194374"},{"date":"08:25 13/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 13/8: Barca v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-138-barca-van-muon-gay-soc-voi-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 13/8.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 138 Barca v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 138 Barca v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Thuc-hu-vu-Barca-mua-Paul-Pogba-voi-gia-130-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Barca v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Goal, Barca v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a M.U d\u00f9 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111ang d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla, Barca \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Pique v\u00e0 Dembele l\u00e0 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 4-0. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Mane l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, Salah v\u00e0 Sturridge m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Man City 0-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. HLV Unai Emery v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Man xanh cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bakayoko r\u1eddi Chelsea ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bakayoko\" title=\"Bakayoko\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Tiemoue-Bakayoko-roi-Chelsea-toi-AC-Milan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bakayoko s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi AC Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tiemoue Bakayoko r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi AC Milan ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-xit-bakayoko-roi-chelsea-ngay-trong-tuan-nay-171-194367.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/25/bom-xit-bakayoko-roi-chelsea-ngay-trong-tuan-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-xit-bakayoko-roi-chelsea-ngay-trong-tuan-nay-171-194367.html\">Bom x\u1ecbt r\u1eddi Chelsea ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</span><br>\r\nTiemoue Bakayoko r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi AC Milan ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Naby Keita?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Naby Keita, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean b\u1edfi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Emery b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City, HLV Unai Emery c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Man City cho th\u1ea5y Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 m\u1edbi v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Gary Neville tin Emery c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Sky Sports, c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean CLB M.U, Gary Neville \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn HLV Unai Emery c\u1ea7n 3, 4 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00f3a s\u1ea1ch &lsquo;di s\u1ea3n&rsquo; m\u00e0 HLV Wenger \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Cech: &quot;Tr\u1eadn thua Man City gi\u00fap Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n&quot;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cech\" title=\"Cech\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cech n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Petr Cech tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates v\u1eeba qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Klopp th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m trung v\u1ec7 Liverpool b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trung v\u1ec7 Dejan Lovren s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 b\u1ee5ng trong v\u00f2ng 3 tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5416","checkdouble":"194373"},{"date":"08:36 13/08","title":"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong ng\u00e0y Barca may m\u1eafn gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/5-diem-nhan-sevilla-12-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n ph\u00fat 78 c\u1ee7a \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba\u201d Ousmane Dembele v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 penalty h\u1ecfng \u0103n c\u1ee7a Sevilla ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, Barcelona m\u1edbi th\u1eafng 2-1 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn Sevilla 1-2 Barca.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>1. Dembele tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng</h2>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n Ousmane Dembele s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Barcelona ch\u1ec9 sau 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barca t\u1eeb Dortmund v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 155 tri\u1ec7u Euro, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p ch\u00ecm trong n\u1ed7i \u0111au ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d c\u00f9ng cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf x\u1ee9 Catalonia.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u00f2n b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Dembele kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Camp Nou. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh sao tr\u1ebb 21 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, Dembele c\u00f2n t\u1ecf ra nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh Messi nh\u01b0 Luis Suarez, Rafinha hay Arthur.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong tr\u1eadn Sevilla 1-2 Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong tr\u1eadn Sevilla 1-2 Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/5-diem-nhan-trong-tran-Sevilla-1-2-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Dembele ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn Sevilla 1-2 Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong hi\u1ec7p 2, Dembele \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5 Sevilla b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 78, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n quan tr\u1ecdng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho Barca. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Vaclik c\u1ee7a Sevilla l\u00e0m n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft ch\u1eebng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Dembele t\u1ea1i Barca. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm c\u1ee7a Blaugrana.</div>\r\n<h2>2. T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR</h2>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a La Liga ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n r\u1eb1ng hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Barcelona v\u00e0 Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb c\u00e1c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a VAR (c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd video) c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong ng\u00e0y Barca may m\u1eafn gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong ng\u00e0y Barca may m\u1eafn gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/5-diem-nhan-trong-ngay-Barca-may-man-gianh-Sieu-cup-TBN-2018-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1edd VAR, Sevilla c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf World Cup 2018, VAR v\u1eabn c\u00f3 sai s\u1ed1, song r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p. V\u00e0 t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn Sevilla 1-2 Barca, n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng. C\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a Sarabia ban \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i bi\u00ean ph\u1ea5t c\u1edd vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb, nh\u01b0ng sau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Carlos Del Cerro nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng VAR, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu l\u00e0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Sevilla s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 minh b\u1ea1ch h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<h2>3. Malcom ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tranh c\u00e3i gi\u1eefa Sevilla v\u00e0 Barca. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ch\u1ec9 1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y (RFEF) \u0111\u00e3 ban h\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec1u lu\u1eadt cho ph\u00e9p hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u01a1n 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c Li\u00ean minh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (EU).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca vs Sevilla Coutinho\" title=\"Barca vs Sevilla Coutinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Barca-vs-Sevilla-Coutinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu EU</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSevilla ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 d\u1ecda s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n n\u1ebfu danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Barca c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00e0 Philippe Coutinho, Malcom, Arthur (Brazil) v\u00e0 Arturo Vidal (Vidal), 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nam M\u1ef9. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u lu\u1eadt m\u00e0 RFEF \u0111\u01b0a ra g\u1ea5p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng cho m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Barca, h\u1ecd l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i r\u1eb1ng Coutinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Blaugrana v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh hy sinh 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nam M\u1ef9 m\u00e0 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Malcom. T\u00e2n binh 41 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay \u1edf lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla. </div>\r\n<h2>4. Suarez th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Luis Suarez kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 14 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. M\u00e3i t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 11, sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mi\u1ec5n l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung \u0110TQG, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y m\u1edbi l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca vs Sevilla Luis Suarez\" title=\"Barca vs Sevilla Luis Suarez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Barca-vs-Sevilla-Luis-Suarez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Luis Suarez m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Suarez c\u00f9ng \u0110T Uruguay d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla, trong s\u1ef1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, s\u1ed1 9 c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c. Anh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 31, n\u1ebfu lo l\u1eafng cho kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Suarez c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eeba. Barca c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh El Pistolero s\u1edbm ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c khi m\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<h2>5. Sevilla kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Sevilla. 3 HLV bao g\u1ed3m Eduardo Berizzo, Vincenzo Montella r\u1ed3i Joaquin Caparros k\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i song \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pablo Machin cua Sevilla\" title=\"Pablo Machin cua Sevilla\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Pablo-Machin-cua-Sevilla.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Machinmang l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi cho Sevilla</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Sevilla ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Caparros v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Pablo Machin. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 43 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 1 n\u0103m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Girona khi gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf n\u1eeda tr\u00ean BXH d\u00f9 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 ban \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ecb li\u1ec7t v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 r\u1edbt h\u1ea1ng cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p \u0111\u01b0a Machin t\u1edbi Sevilla. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t Los Hispalenses r\u1ec7u r\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Barca ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf trong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha. N\u1ebfu Wissam Ben Yedder th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 11m \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e2ng c\u00fap.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Sevilla 1-2 Barca (Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN 2018):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/13/Sevilla-vs-Barcelona.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Sevilla 1-2 Barca tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/vo-dich-sieu-cup-lionel-messi-lap-ky-luc-moi-trong-mau-ao-barca-180-194357.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau C\u00fap, Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/sevilla-vs-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018-dem-nay-372-194340.html\">Sevilla 1-2 Barca: Messi v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chot-tuong-lai-ousmane-dembele-180-194312.html\">Barca ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ousmane Dembele</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sevilla-to-cao-barca-truoc-sieu-cup-tay-ban-nha-180-194300.html\">Sevilla t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u00ean v\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5415","checkdouble":"194361"},{"date":"07:19 13/08","title":"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/thay-gi-sau-tran-thang-tung-bung-cua-liverpool-truoc-west-ham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, CLB Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 West Ham. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>1. H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Liverpool qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 &lsquo;n\u00e9m&rsquo; v\u00e0o TTCN h\u01a1n 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y song HLV Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o cho tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1eabn qu\u00e1 &lsquo;kh\u1ee7ng&rsquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Firmino c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 70 nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Liverpool khi Salah m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1, Mane ghi 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Sturridge \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng trong l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a The Kop v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha xu\u1ed1ng bi\u00ean nhanh \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, hay nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ee7 tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Salah l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t pha b\u0103ng c\u1eaft \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang t\u1eeb h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Robertson.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool thang West Ham trong tran mo man Premier League 2018-19.\" title=\"Liverpool th\u1eafng West Ham trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018-19.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/liverpool-thang-west-ham-doi-bong-manh-nhat-da-lo-dien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV&nbsp;Klopp</em><em>&nbsp;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ecbp ph\u00f4 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1edf tr\u1eadn&nbsp;Liverpool 4-0 West Ham</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, b\u00e0n nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Sadio Mane c\u0169ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng. \u0110\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 ba, Mane nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe c\u1ee7a Firmino \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha ra ch\u00e2n quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n gi\u00fap The Kop ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Daniel Sturridge l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m cho th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a Liverpool th\u00eam lung linh tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Firmino ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh song v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield. S\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1eddi khi n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Liverpool m\u00f9a n\u00e0y ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p t\u1eeb b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Salah-Mane-Firmino. V\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd \u0111ang &lsquo;bay cao&rsquo;, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 v\u1eadt c\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee7 n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn The Kop ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh Liverpool<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c ca ng\u1ee3i Salah hay Mane, ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Keita \u1edf tr\u1eadn&nbsp;Liverpool 4-0 West Ham.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Naby Keita v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 52,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng cho th\u1ea5y n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng lao l\u00ean khi c\u1ea7n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Guinea \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Liverpool.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0y c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y trong c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Keita ra mat Liver\" title=\"tien ve Keita ra mat Liver\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/tien-ve-Keita-ra-mat-Liver.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Naby Keita c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Anfield&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh Keita, t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Anfield. T\u1eebng khi\u1ebfn The Kop ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i Anfield. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 qua tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Alisson \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng Liverpool c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n James Milner<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Milner\" title=\"James Milner\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/3-1534086807304455525124.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>James Milner cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Liverpool</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 32, James Milner v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Milner c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i hay theo tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p West Ham, Milner \u0111\u00e3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, James Milner \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 93% s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1edbi pha nho\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Robertson \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o trong cho Mane tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i James Milner \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf cu\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap b\u1ea1c Premier League c\u00f9ng Liverpool l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i Pellegrini<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong l\u1ea7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, HLV Pellegrini \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 West Ham. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb &lsquo;b\u00f3p ngh\u1eb9t&rsquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 trang b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u &lsquo;binh h\u00f9ng&rsquo; \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y khi b\u1ecf v\u00e0o TTCN s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng mang t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh &lsquo;B\u00faa t\u1ea1&rsquo; tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a The Kop.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Manuel Pellegrini sau tran thua Liverpool thua nhan West Ham xung dang phai nhan ket qua nay.\" title=\"HLV Manuel Pellegrini sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn West Ham x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/hlv-manuel-pellegrini-sau-tran-thua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Manuel Pellegrini c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i v\u1edbi West Ham sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">West Ham ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng 35% v\u00e0 tung ra 5 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Liverpool. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi West Ham c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Liverpool song d\u1eabu sao m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HLV Pellegrini trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Arsenal, Man Utd v\u00e0 Chelsea t\u1eeb nay \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 9, xem ch\u1eebng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean TTCN.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sterling-ly-giai-man-an-mung-khieu-khich-o-tran-gap-arsenal-172-194350.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/sterling-ly-giai-man-an-mung-khieu-khich-o-tran-gap-arsenal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sterling-ly-giai-man-an-mung-khieu-khich-o-tran-gap-arsenal-172-194350.html\">Sterling l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng khi\u00eau kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</span><br>\r\nRaheem Sterling t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon-172-194349.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon-172-194349.html\">Cech: Tr\u1eadn thua Man City gi\u00fap Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Petr Cech tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates v\u1eeba qua.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-giup-liverpool-vui-dap-west-ham-4-ban-khong-go-172-194348.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/3-ly-do-giup-liverpool-vui-dap-west-ham-4-ban-khong-go.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-ly-do-giup-liverpool-vui-dap-west-ham-4-ban-khong-go-172-194348.html\">3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u00f9i d\u1eadp West Ham 4 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1</span><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-0. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y r\u1eaby t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi The Kop. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-manuel-pellegrini-sau-tran-thua-liverpool-172-194343.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/hlv-manuel-pellegrini-sau-tran-thua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-manuel-pellegrini-sau-tran-thua-liverpool-172-194343.html\">HLV Manuel Pellegrini: Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t Premier League</span><br>\r\nHLV Manuel Pellegrini sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn West Ham ch\u01a1i ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t, x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-arsenal-vs-man-city-02-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194346.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/clip-arsenal-vs-man-city-02-highlights-premier-league-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-arsenal-vs-man-city-02-highlights-premier-league-2018-326-194346.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Arsenal 0-2 Man City (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19)</span><br>\r\nMan City ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5414","checkdouble":"194364"},{"date":"07:50 13/08","title":"HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Naby Keita?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-mat-an-tuong-cua-naby-keita.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Naby Keita, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean b\u1edfi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Klopp khen ng\u1ee3i Naby Keita</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i West Ham v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0, qua \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Sadio Mane l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, Mohamed Salah v\u00e0&nbsp;Daniel Sturridge m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf ra m\u1eaft ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Naby Keita h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Naby Keita h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-mat-an-tuong-cua-naby-keita.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Naby Keita ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-liverpool-vs-west-ham-1282018-172-194329.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool 4-0 West Ham</span>, t\u00e2n binh Naby Keita \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV klopp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t khi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Anh gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Naby Keita, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean b\u1edfi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Sau 6 tu\u1ea7n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n m\u1edbi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. H\u00f4m nay, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Naby Keita. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00edch nghi r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 CLB n\u00e0o. Naby Keita c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c nhau, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 8 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Keita c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xung quanh, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e0ng gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Milner c\u0169ng ca ng\u1ee3i Naby Keita</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i HLV Klopp, James Milner c\u0169ng ca ng\u1ee3i Naby Keita. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Naby Keita\" title=\"Naby Keita\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Naby Keita \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Klopp v\u00e0 Milner h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin, Keita cho th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Keita c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n n\u1eefa trong v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i h\u01a1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111a n\u0103ng, Keita c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;S\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Liverpool \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, \u0111i\u1ec1u gi\u00fap khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n. B\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5413","checkdouble":"194366"},{"date":"08:03 13/08","title":"\"Bom x\u1ecbt\" r\u1eddi Chelsea ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/25/bom-xit-bakayoko-roi-chelsea-ngay-trong-tuan-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tiemoue Bakayoko r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi AC Milan ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan quan t\u00e2m Tiemoue Bakayoko</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 Nemanja Matic t\u1edbi M.U, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1eeb Monaco. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Tiemoue-Bakayoko-roi-Chelsea-toi-AC-Milan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bakayoko l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a AC Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994, hi\u1ec7n Bakayoko \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Stamford Bridge. V\u1edbi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trong tay, HLV Sarri \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Monaco.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Bakayoko kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea, m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ac-milan-nang-gia-hoi-mua-bakayoko-172-193993.html\" target=\"_blank\">AC Milan mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Tiemoue Bakayoko</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>AC Milan s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Bakayoko</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tiemoue Bakayoko r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi AC Milan ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bakayoko choi rat tot trong nhung tran dau gan day\" title=\"Bakayoko ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/9/bakayoko-chi-roi-chelsea-neu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bakayoko s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho AC Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, AC Milan s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u01b0\u1ee3n Tiemoue Bakayoko r\u1eddi \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 theo ESPN, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a The Blues c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Italia, Bakayoko s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Chelsea, song t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao. Bakayoko \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o AC Milan.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5412","checkdouble":"194367"},{"date":"07:35 13/08","title":"Pep n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/pep-noi-gi-ve-chien-thang-truoc-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u00f4m Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt v\u1eeba qua.</h2><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Pep n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal?</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi Man City khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 2-0 chung cu\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Arsenal. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Arsenal. V\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 14 ph\u00fat sau khi b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Raheem Sterling.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bernardo Silva ghi ban cho Man City\" title=\"Bernardo Silva ghi ban cho Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-pep-team-khong-ngu-quen-tren-chien-thang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Pep khen ng\u1ee3i c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, Man City \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi Arsenal bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i v\u00f9ng l\u00ean, tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 th\u00eam 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i: &quot;Kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Arsenal. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi sau h\u01a1n 20 n\u0103m, v\u00e0 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. Do \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eddi khen v\u00ec chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u00f2n kh\u00e1t khao chinh ph\u1ee5c danh hi\u1ec7u NHA, Pep n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &quot;N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 c\u00f3. V\u1eady n\u00ean m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn ra \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang hay kh\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu Man City b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i Emirates, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Huddersfield Town \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Man xanh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Highlight: Arsenal 0-2 Man City (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\">\t</span></em></p>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278994\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/13/arsenal-mancity-.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-thuyet-phuc-cua-man-city-truoc-arsenal-172-194359.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/5-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-thuyet-phuc-cua-man-city-truoc-arsenal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-thuyet-phuc-cua-man-city-truoc-arsenal-172-194359.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</span><br>\r\nNgay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Arsenal, Man City \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2-0. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon-172-194349.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cech-thua-man-city-giup-arsenal-truong-thanh-hon-172-194349.html\">Cech: Tr\u1eadn thua Man City gi\u00fap Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Petr Cech tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates v\u1eeba qua.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-arsenal-02-man-city-172-194347.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-arsenal-02-man-city.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-arsenal-02-man-city-172-194347.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Arsenal 0-2 Man City</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Arsenal 0-2 Man City v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sterling-ly-giai-man-an-mung-khieu-khich-o-tran-gap-arsenal-172-194350.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/sterling-ly-giai-man-an-mung-khieu-khich-o-tran-gap-arsenal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sterling-ly-giai-man-an-mung-khieu-khich-o-tran-gap-arsenal-172-194350.html\">Sterling l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng khi\u00eau kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</span><br>\r\nRaheem Sterling t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n World Cup...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5411","checkdouble":"194368"},{"date":"08:36 13/08","title":"HLV Emery n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Cech v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Leno?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/10/hlv-emery-noi-gi-ve-quyet-dinh-su-dung-cech-va-loai-bo-leno.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Unai Emery n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao ch\u1ecdn Petr Cech v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Leno trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Emery khuy\u00ean Leno ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn ch\u1edd c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i qua, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/arsenal-vs-man-city-ngoai-hang-anh-1282018-372-194327.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp Man City</span> trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y d\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Arsenal sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Arsenal sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/HLV-Unai-Emery-noi-ve-Arsenal-sau-tran-thua-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Emery l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i sao ch\u1ecdn Cech thay v\u00ec Leno</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi CH S\u00e9c c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Laporte hay Aguero.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao ch\u1ecdn Petr Cech v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Leno trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCech c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. H\u00f4m nay, C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, Cech \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Leno v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp r\u1ea5t nhanh, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Emery n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City, Ainsley Maitland-Niles r\u1eddi s\u00e2n t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm sau pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Kyle Walker. Anh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Stephan Lichtsteiner, n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Maitland-Niles, HLV Emery chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep danh gia cao Arsenal cua Emery\" title=\"Pep \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/pep.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Emery n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00fang m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 Maitland-Niles g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eefa\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cSead Kolasinac v\u1eabn ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, Monreal \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5410","checkdouble":"194371"},{"date":"19:52 12/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2><span style=\"display: none;\" id=\"1534078193167S\">\u00a0</span>HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D c\u00f9ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia v\u00e0 Bahrain.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang n\u1eafm gi\u1eef t\u1ea5m HCV m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam \u1edf k\u1ef3 ASIAD 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u00fang ta x\u1ebfp nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D c\u00f2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E, hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><em>HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ea3m ngh\u0129 n\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi h\u00e3ng th\u00f4ng t\u1ea5n Yonhap: \u201cN\u1ebfu Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00ean l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng e s\u1ee3 n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, m\u00e1i \u1ea5m gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb trang Yonhap News cho bi\u1ebft, HLV Kim Hak Bum s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2 cho Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf ASIAD 18. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Kim chi \u0111ang li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n d\u1ef1a theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y \u1edf trung t\u00e2m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c gia t\u1ea1i Paju (ph\u00eda B\u1eafc Seoul).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Pakistan v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 14/8, hai ng\u00e0y sau h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p Nepal tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hai-doi-hinh-toi-uu-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-194100.html\">Hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n<o:RelyOnVML />\r\n<o:AllowPNG />\r\n</o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<w:WordDocument>\r\n<w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n<w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n<w:TrackMoves />\r\n<w:TrackFormatting />\r\n<w:PunctuationKerning />\r\n<w:ValidateAgainstSchemas />\r\n<w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n<w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n<w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n<w:DoNotPromoteQF />\r\n<w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOther>\r\n<w:LidThemeAsian>JA</w:LidThemeAsian>\r\n<w:LidThemeComplexScript>X-NONE</w: