tent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 do b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5.</h2><h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Pakistan v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 14/8 t\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0o \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Su\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Indonesia \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tham d\u1ef1 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 18, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/39008871_259135861477987_1418586766830469120_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp chay do b\u1ecb n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5. \u1ea2nh: Sport5</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i r\u00e8n qu\u00e2n \u1edf s\u00e2n Sutasoma 2 - \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n Cikarang Haper kho\u1ea3ng 50 c\u00e2y s\u1ed1. T\u00ednh ra, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 100 c\u00e2y s\u1ed1 cho c\u1ea3 \u0111i c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi gi\u1edd gi\u1ea5c sinh ho\u1ea1t, luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o khi h\u1ecd b\u1ecb \u2018tra t\u1ea5n\u2019 do ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng xa nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, khi m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp th\u00ec Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ASIAD 2018 l\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eeb 18h00 theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ban \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 20h00. L\u00fd do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda BTC \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp v\u00e0o khung 18h00.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp mu\u1ed9n 2 gi\u1edd c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edd gi\u1ea5c \u0103n t\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. Do \u0111\u00f3, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i b\u00e3i \u0111\u1ea5t tr\u1ed1ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00e0nh n\u00e0y, c\u00e1n b\u1ed9 VFF \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi AFC \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebfu s\u00f3t trong kh\u00e2u t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia. Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc-168-194334.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc-168-194334.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\n<span>Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n<o:RelyOnVML />\r\n<o:AllowPNG />\r\n</o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<w:WordDocument>\r\n<w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n<w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n<w:TrackMoves />\r\n<w:TrackFormatting />\r\n<w:PunctuationKerning />\r\n<w:ValidateAgainstSchemas />\r\n<w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n<w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n<w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n<w:DoNotPromoteQF />\r\n<w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOther>\r\n<w:LidThemeAsian>JA</w:LidThemeAsian>\r\n<w:LidThemeComplexScript>X-NONE</w:LidThemeComplexScript>\r\n<w:Compatibility>\r\n<w:BreakWrappedTables />\r\n<w:SnapToGridInCell />\r\n<w:WrapTextWithPunct />\r\n<w:UseAsianBreakRules />\r\n<w:DontGrowAutofit />\r\n<w:SplitPgBreakAndParaMark />\r\n<w:EnableOpenTypeKerning />\r\n<w:DontFlipMirrorIndents />\r\n<w:OverrideTableStyleHps />\r\n<w:UseFELayout />\r\n</w:Compatibility>\r\n<m:mathPr>\r\n<m:mathFont m:val=\"Cambria Math\" />\r\n<m:brkBin m:val=\"before\" />\r\n<m:brkBinSub m:val=\"--\" />\r\n<m:smallFrac m:val=\"off\" />\r\n<m:dispDef />\r\n<m:lMargin m:val=\"0\" />\r\n<m:rMargin m:val=\"0\" />\r\n<m:defJc m:val=\"centerGroup\" />\r\n<m:wrapIndent m:val=\"1440\" />\r\n<m:intLim m:val=\"subSup\" />\r\n